content.html: My dad is not remotely “woke” or online, so I asked him: “Dad, what do you think about Leo only dating women under 25 even though he’s almost 50?” “It’s gross.” 🤷🏻‍♀️ this is not a “new feminist complaint,” it’s actually common sense, to decent people.
content.value:
My dad is not remotely “woke” or online, so I asked him:

“Dad, what do you think about Leo only dating women under 25 even though he’s almost 50?”
“It’s gross.”

🤷🏻‍♀️ this is not a “new feminist complaint,” it’s actually common sense, to decent people.
